statements: SELECT id, user_id, page_id, visit_time, action_taken, device_type FROM website_analytics;
SELECT * FROM website_analytics WHERE user_id = 123;
SELECT count(*) FROM website_analytics WHERE device_type = 'mobile';
SELECT page_id, visit_time FROM website_analytics WHERE action_taken = 'click' ORDER BY visit_time DESC;
SELECT id, user_id, action_taken FROM website_analytics WHERE visit_time >= '2022-01-01' AND visit_time <= '2022-01-31';
SELECT * FROM website_analytics WHERE user_id = 10 ORDER BY visit_time DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT user_id, COUNT(*) AS visit_count FROM website_analytics GROUP BY user_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 1 ORDER BY visit_count DESC;
SELECT page_id, COUNT(DISTINCT user_id) AS unique_visitors FROM website_analytics GROUP BY page_id ORDER BY unique_visitors DESC;
SELECT AVG(UNIX_TIMESTAMP(visit_time)) AS avg_unix_timestamp FROM website_analytics;
SELECT * FROM website_analytics WHERE device_type = 'Mobile' AND action_taken = 'purchase' ORDER BY visit_time ASC;
SELECT * FROM website_traffic ORDER BY visit_timestamp DESC;

SELECT visit_id, page_visited, visitor_id FROM website_traffic WHERE visit_timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31'
SELECT visitor_id, visitor_name, last_visit FROM user_behavior WHERE visitor_name LIKE 'J%' ORDER BY last_visit DESC

SELECT page_visited, SUM(unique_visitors) AS total_unique_visitors FROM page_metrics GROUP BY page_visited HAVING total_unique_visitors > 100 ORDER BY total_unique_visitors DESC;

SELECT uv.page_visited, uv.unique_visitors, tm.total_visits FROM page_metrics AS uv INNER JOIN page_metrics AS tm ON uv.page_visited = tm.page_visited AND uv.unique_visitors > tm.total_visits ORDER BY uv.unique_visitors DESC;
